Lemon blueberry avocado smoothie is such a delicious, easy, and filling breakfast idea. Blueberries are an excellent source of fiber, antioxidants, and micronutrients like vitamin C, K, B6 and manganese. Lemons are a good source of fiber, antioxidantsÂ  and vitamin C. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 Using a zester or grater, zest the entire peel of one lemon. Then, cut the lemon and juice one half. Step 2 Add all ingredients to a high-speed blender, starting with the milk of choice. Step 3 Blend on high until smooth and creamy. Feel free to add flavours or amounts of liquid until desired taste or consistency is reached.